\begin_layout Standard
对于狄拉克方程，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & i\left(\gamma^{0}\partial_{t}+\sbf\gamma\cdot\nabla\psi\right)=m\psi\\
\text{左乘}\gamma^{0}\text{得到}\quad & i\partial_{t}\psi\left(t\right)=H\psi\left(t\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $H=-i\gamma^{0}\sbf\gamma\cdot\nabla+\gamma^{0}m$
\end_inset

。我们想得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
