\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

待定。如果有
\begin_inset Formula $T^{-1}HT=H$
\end_inset

，即
\begin_inset Formula $\overrightarrow{K}U^{-1}HU\overrightarrow{K}=H$
\end_inset

，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
